HEADWORD: Maldon
<hw>Maldon</hw> <pos>prop. n.</pos> <def>A battle in which the Danes
defeated the East Saxons in 991; it is celebrated in an old English
poem.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> battle of Maldon.</syn>⟦br⟧
